<HL>
   Bond Unit Extends Offer
</HL>
<DATE>
09/18/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C19
</SO>
<CO>
   A.BON
</CO>
<IN>
BOND MARKET NEWS (BON)
DISTILLERS AND BREWERS, MAKERS OF ALCOHOLIC BEVERAGES (DST)
BEVERAGES (BVG)
</IN>
<LP>
   PERTH, Western Australia -- Bond Brewing Holdings Ltd.
said its subsidiary, Dimola Pty., has extended its offer to
purchase as much as 90% of Bond's principal amount
outstanding of 12 5/8% extendable subordinated debentures to
midnight EDT Friday.
   The depositary has advised Bond and Dimola that, as of
noon EDT last Friday, about 8.5% of the outstanding principal
amount of debentures had been tendered to the depositary.
